---
title: Persian Spiced Vegetable Bowl (v) with Coriander Drizzle, Crispy Onions and Feta
description: We love a good Vegetable Bowl with Onions and Feta and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/persian-spiced-vegetable-bowl-0323fc43-970fa3a4.jpg
